Description: Typical range for ns fiber lasers cleaning delicate organics like wood to avoid charring; starting at 100W balances efficiency and safety. Source: Manufacturer specs from IPG Photonics for 1064 nm systems; academic review in 'Laser Cleaning of Wood Surfaces' (Journal of Cultural Heritage, 2018).
